title: League COSPLAYERS of DragonCon 2014 by Minhnhat
body:
Hi everyone,
I made this Cosplay Music Video with League cosplayers during Dragoncon 2014.
And I wanted to share my work with you guys.
I hope you will all enjoy it :D
[League COSPLAYERS of DragonCon 2014](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lo7lrxiiXFI)

Also here's a list of all the cosplayers in the video as far as I know :

replies.body: THIS IS AWESOME I love the pauses after each feature--so good!!
HOLY CRAP ALL OF THE AMAZING COSPLAY! I ABSOLUTELY LOVE THIS!
That was a really cool and creative video. That Mr. Fishbones that Jinx has was perfect. I loved the Genderbent Vi voiceover too. Looks like the cosplay at Dragoncon was top notch.
I was there as Pool Party Graves. And I didn't even get in the video :(
Male Vi, Female Ezreal, and that Zed cosplay were amazing!
Most excellent cosplays.  A lot of effort and great results!

I found teemo good people, cosplay facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/sleepingforestcosplaygroup/timeline?ref=page_internal
Yay! Awesome video! I always love the League only cosplay videos from cons! Those were all great cosplays! My favorites were genderbent Vi and Snowstorm Sivir!

GREAT editing, nice filmwork. Make more! hue

I think the Snowstorm Sivir was my personal favorite
